 Securing the gold at Rio 2016 became the biggest highlight in Schooling's career.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"/CFP\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest highlight\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"Schooling's career\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He never stood on the Olympic podium again and did not qualify for the 2023 Asian Games.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic podium\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 Asian Games\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nonetheless, the 28-year-old will still be remembered as one of the greatest athletes in Singapore's history with one Olympic gold, three Asian Games titles and 29 Southeast Asian Games championships.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9758940381763054, \"rank\": 0.024701247585695498, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the greatest athletes\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"one Olympic gold\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While I am stepping away from competing, swimming will forever be a part of who I am,\\\" Schooling said.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"Schooling\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has given me a platform to inspire others to chase their dreams, no matter the odds.\", \"from\": 1865, \"